refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
&style.oop;
public trueIntlCalendar::setFirstDayOfWeek intdayOfWeek
&style.procedural;
trueintlcal_set_first_day_of_week IntlCalendarcalendar intdayOfWeek
週の始まりとみなされる曜日を定義します。 これは、 IntlCalendar::FIELD_WEEK_OF_YEAR や IntlCalendar::FIELD_YEAR_WOY のような、 週の始まりと終わりの概念に依存したフィールドの振る舞いに影響します。

&reftitle.parameters;
calendar
&intl.parameter.intl-calendar;
dayOfWeek
IntlCalendar::DOW_SUNDAY, IntlCalendar::DOW_MONDAY, …, IntlCalendar::DOW_SATURDAY のうちのいずれか。

  &reftitle.examples;



   IntlCalendar::setFirstDayOfWeek


<?php
ini_set('date.timezone', 'Europe/Lisbon');
ini_set('intl.default_locale', 'es_ES');

$cal = IntlCalendar::createInstance();
$cal->set(2013, 5 /* June */, 30); // A Sunday

var_dump($cal->getFirstDayOfWeek()); // 2 (Monday)

echo IntlDateFormatter::formatObject($cal, <<<EOD
'local day of week: 'cc'
week of month    : 'W'
week of year     : 'ww
EOD
), "\n";

$cal->setFirstDayOfWeek(IntlCalendar::DOW_SUNDAY);

echo IntlDateFormatter::formatObject($cal, <<<EOD
'local day of week: 'cc'
week of month    : 'W'
week of year     : 'ww
EOD
), "\n";


    &example.outputs;


int(2)
local day of week: 7
week of month    : 4
week of year     : 26
local day of week: 1
week of month    : 5
week of year     : 27
